UID:ffe5d4fe-656f-538f-82db-6c3d446d368e
SUMMARY:Community-Centered Connectivity Grant Program
DESCRIPTION:The Internet Society Foundation’s Community-Centered Connectivity (CCC) 
 Grant Program\, a core part of the Internet Society’s work to help commu
 nities bridge the digital divide\, aims to address these challenges by s
 upporting organizations to develop and expand Internet access and increa
 se adoption in digitally excluded communities.
URL:https://www.isocfoundation.org/grant-programme/community-centered-connectivity/
DTSTAMP:20240101T000000Z
DTSTART;VALUE=DATE:20260507
DTEND;VALUE=DATE:20260507
