DESCRIPTION:A six-month program equipping 20 professionals with the skills\, knowled
 ge\, and tools to improve local Internet interconnection infrastructure 
 and advocate for policies that make Internet access more affordable\, re
 liable\, and resilient.
URL:https://www.internetsociety.org/fellowships/peering/
